Package masterclass

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AskForData
    Responsible for the view of "Personal data" window.
    ConfirmListener
    Reads user personal data from jTextFields and makes new database record.
    Exercise
    Stores data from database about user: name, surname, type of collision.
    FinishListener
    Implements confirm button listener.
    FitListener
    Fits gauss and polynomial functions for selected dataset with fitting ranges set by user.
    GetDataListener
    Implements listener to read and get data from "Personal data" window.
    Histo
    Responsible for general view of the program.
    Listeners
    Implements listeners, used in the program.
    SliderListener
    Manages and stores ranges(min,max) for fitted functions.
    User
    Stores and manages output format for data.
